s:751:"<p>This course is a self-study space where you can brush-up your English. The integration of the 4 skills and the 21 C skills is an important asset. It is task-based, learner-centered &amp; objective-oriented. You are invited to benefit the multi-media tools and strategies in order to improve you communication skills, too. It is in line with what you learn using your textbook and other resources that your teacher decides are convenient for your learning steps. You are supposed to spend at least <b>25 </b>hours on your self-study tasks &amp; you have <b>5</b> hours of synchronous audio sessions with the tutor. Every week, you have one hour with the tutor in order to have opportunities to discuss, learn &amp; practise.Â </p><p>WELCOME ! :)</p>";